"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-27-athletes-bite-medals-olympics-ritual-explained-21256238\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"TheParis 2024 Olympicswill see 10,000 of the finest athletes in the world battling it out over 32 sports across 19 action-packed days.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheParis\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 8}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicswill\", \"from\": 14, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"the finest athletes\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 60}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 73}, {\"ngram\": \"over 32 sports\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"19 action-packed days\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of each event, thegold, silver and bronze medallistsare presented with their prizes, posing for pictures on the podium in what is one of the proudest moments in their lives.\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 146}, {\"ngram\": \"each event\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medallistsare\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"their prizes\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"the proudest moments\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what might seem a little odd is the customary pose involving athletes biting their medals.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the customary pose\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"their medals\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics The practice has become common in everyone from Olympians toPremier Leaguefootballers.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"latest news\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"The practice\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"Leaguefootballers\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But why exactly do athletes bite their medals?\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"their medals\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reason for athletes gnawing into their gold, silver and bronze medals has changed over time.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reason\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"their gold, silver and bronze medals\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Traditionally, because gold is softer and more malleable than other metals, one way to determine whether or not it was real gold was to bite into it - if it's authentic, your teeth would have left an indentation.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"other metals\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"one way\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"real gold\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"your teeth\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"an indentation\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, most medal winners are not going to be too hung up on if it's actual gold or not as it's what the medal symbolises that matters.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most medal winners\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"actual gold\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For what it's worth, Olympic gold medals are not full gold.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"full gold\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are required to be made from at least 92.5% silver, and must contain a minimum of six grams of gold.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"at least 92.5% silver\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"six grams\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So why do they still chow down into their medal?\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their medal\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's all about the optics, of course.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the optics\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's become an obsession with the photographers,' David Wallechinsky, president of the International Society of Olympic Historians, toldCNN.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wallechinsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Wallechinsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wallechinsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Wallechinsky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an obsession\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the photographers\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Society\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Historians\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"toldCNN\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think they look at it as an iconic shot, as something that you can probably sell.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an iconic shot\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think it's something the athletes would probably do on their own.'\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Noah Lyles can back up bold claims with victory in the Olympic 100metres final ArrowMORE:Fans are obsessed with Snoop Dogg's 'dope' Olympics pin that's so on-brand for the rapper ArrowMORE:Olympics fans praise Hayden Wilde's classy reaction to epic Alex Yee triathlon win Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour